Name: Silvermane Lieutenant
Desc: The leader of a squad of Belobog's Silvermane Guards.\nSilvermane Lieutenants can raise a giant shield during combat and Enhance themselves. Attacking a Silvermane Lieutenant with their shield raised will immediately result in a fierce Counter.

SkillList.SkillDesc: Deals Physical DMG to a single target.
Deals massive Physical DMG to a single target.
Enters the Counter state. When attacked by a single character, acts immediately and casts "Pierce" on the attacker.
Summons Silvermane Soldiers or Silvermane Gunners
